---

<style>
    section {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    h2 {
        color: #281480;
        text-align: center;

        font-size: 2.25rem;

        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.1; /* 2.475rem */

        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .faqs {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
